      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> friends,</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> We’ve set up a cool system using <a href=\"https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=msquare\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a> to help manage your tasks and files. Here’s how it works:</p>\n<p>1.Change Status in <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/spiral_calendar.png?v=12\" title=\":spiral_calendar:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":spiral_calendar:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nWhen you change the status to “Planned” in <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>, it triggers our automation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://2.Search\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">2.Search</a> Google Drive <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/mag.png?v=12\" title=\":mag:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":mag:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nIt checks Google Drive to see if a folder already exists.</p>\n<p>3.Look Inside Folders <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/open_file_folder.png?v=12\" title=\":open_file_folder:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":open_file_folder:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nIf the folder exists, it searches for a file matching the <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> item. If not, it creates a new folder.</p>\n<p>4.Create New Folder <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nIf the file isn’t there, a new folder with the <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> item name is created.</p>\n<p>5.Update Link in <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/link.png?v=12\" title=\":link:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":link:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nIt updates the Google Drive link column in <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> with the folder’s web link.</p>\n<p>6.Automatic Folder Creation <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/file_folder.png?v=12\" title=\":file_folder:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":file_folder:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nA new Google Drive folder is created to keep everything organized.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Benefits:<br />\nAutomatic folder and file management.<br />\nReal-time updates to your <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> board.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/wrench.png?v=12\" title=\":wrench:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wrench:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Try it now and boost your productivity! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/8/0/8089e858050f6b3decb6bb8e39b668887ae16900.jpeg\" title=\"monday\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/8/0/8089e858050f6b3decb6bb8e39b668887ae16900_2_690x311.jpeg\" alt=\"monday\" width=\"690\" height=\"311\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">monday</span><span class=\"informations\">1835×828 45.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>If you require additional assistance, please don’t hesitate to reach out to us.<br />\n<a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MSquare Support</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/msquareautomation-live\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Book Live Implementation</a><br />\nVisit us <a href=\"https://www.msquare.pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqidlIIwbejxZmRUWBICcjQ\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Youtube Channel</a></p>"
